</ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>unique Character Style</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Manoeuver through space stations with a non physical body. Your LIFE is your BOOST which is your CURRENCY, spend it wisely</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1258960/extras/e60ef0d9616c81402b5e24e86ed0f76b.poster.avif?t=1716635190\" width=800 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1258960/extras/e60ef0d9616c81402b5e24e86ed0f76b.webm?t=1716635190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1258960/extras/e60ef0d9616c81402b5e24e86ed0f76b.mp4?t=1716635190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
